data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This exquisite 3 bedroom, 1 bathroom residence has been tastefully updated throughout. The eat-in kitchen is a culinary masterpiece, featuring sleek granite countertops that add a touch of elegance. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the kitchen to the living room, which boasts vaulted ceilings and beautiful beams, creating a spacious and inviting atmosphere. Step outside onto the large, covered patio and enjoy the perfect space for outdoor entertaining or relaxation. The spacious pantry provides ample storage, keeping your kitchen organized and clutter-free. But that's not all – the backyard offers a delightful surprise with a 15x20 out building, providing a versatile space for hobbies, relaxation, or entertaining. This home is truly a gem, combining modern updates with thoughtful design elements that will exceed your expectations. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your forever home!
